data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Beech Grove neighborhood, this elegant 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom, two-story residence boasts a 12 by 14 foot deck. Recent upgrades include a newer roof, hot water heater, furnace with a heat pump AC unit, and modern windows. Enjoy the privacy of the fenced yard with mature trees, complemented by two sheds and a fire pit. A finished basement adds flexibility, while included appliances (dishwasher, refrigerator, garbage disposal) add convenience. Regions Bank offers a 100% financing option for eligible buyers. Schedule a showing today to explore this inviting property.
